data.description: Original family member is offering this wonderful solid brick bungalow home with a concrete side driveway. Located on a quiet street with well-kept homes. Newer roof, windows and updated main bathroom make this home a must see. A total of 4 bedrooms (3 on the main level) and 3 full bathrooms helps accommodate a large family or related living. Hardwood floors and spacious room sizes throughout. Ideally located near shopping, restaurants, and expressways. Although this is a well-maintained home, it is being sold "as is". Make your appointment today before it's SOLD!!!
